data.description: ASSUMABLE VA LOAN at 2.375%?  Beautiful two-story home nestled within the charming community of Northeast Crossing with an affordable HOA! The open floor plan welcomes you with a seamlessly integrated island kitchen boasting granite countertops, a tumbled stone backsplash, and a delightful box window illuminating the dining area with natural light. Step into the stunning two-story living room, where multiple windows flood the space with warmth and brightness. First floor primary suite, featuring a bay window that adds character and charm, along with a spacious walk-in closet, double vanity, and a luxurious walk-in shower adorned with tile surround. Upstairs, a generously sized loft offers versatile living space, perfect for a media room, game area, or home office. Accompanied by two bedrooms and a full bath, this level provides ample room for comfort and privacy. Outside, the covered patio overlooks a privacy fenced yard and a convenient storage shed for added functionality. Conveniently located near major highways, military bases, shopping, and entertainment, this home offers unparalleled convenience for modern lifestyles.
